<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Boost CV — Master GFF 2027</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;700;800&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  :root {
    --bg: #080a0d;
    --surface: #10131a;
    --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    --text: #e8eaf0;
    --muted: #5a607a;
    --muted2: #9298b0;
    --toeic: #7c6dfa;
    --toeic2: #a594ff;
    --excel: #2d9e6b;
    --excel2: #4dcc8f;
    --amf: #f59e0b;
    --amf2: #fbbf24;
  }
  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 40px 20px;
  }
  .container { max-width: 560px; width: 100%; }
  .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .eyebrow {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  h1 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .sub { font-size: 15px; color: var(--muted2); line-height: 1.6; }

  .cards { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }

  .card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 22px 24px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 14px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.18s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.18s;
  }
  .card.toeic::before { background: radial-gradient(ellipse at left, rgba(124,109,250,0.08), transparent 70%); }
  .card.excel::before { background: radial-gradient(ellipse at left, rgba(45,158,107,0.08), transparent 70%); }
  .card.amf::before { background: radial-gradient(ellipse at left, rgba(245,158,11,0.08), transparent 70%); }
  .card:hover { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }

  .card-icon {
    font-size: 28px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 52px; height: 52px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }

  .card-body { flex: 1; }
  .card-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 3px;
  }
  .card-sub { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted2); }

  .card-badge {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .card.toeic .card-badge { background: rgba(124,109,250,0.15); color: var(--toeic2); border: 1px solid rgba(124,109,250,0.3); }
  .card.excel .card-badge { background: rgba(45,158,107,0.15); color: var(--excel2); border: 1px solid rgba(45,158,107,0.3); }
  .card.amf .card-badge { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.12); color: var(--amf2); border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.25); }

  .card.disabled { opacity: 0.45; pointer-events: none; cursor: default; }

  .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <div class="header">
    <div class="eyebrow">Boost CV · Master GFF 2027</div>
    <h1>Tes certifications</h1>
    <p class="sub">3 certifs · 1 été · Clique sur celle du jour.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="cards">
    <a href="toeic_app.html" class="card toeic">
      <div class="card-icon">🎯</div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-title">TOEIC 850</div>
        <div class="card-sub">22 mai → juillet 2026 · 70 jours</div>
      </div>
      <span class="card-badge">EN COURS</span>
    </a>

    <a href="excel_app.html" class="card excel">
      <div class="card-icon">📊</div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-title">Excel MOS / TOSA</div>
        <div class="card-sub">1er → 20 juin 2026 · 20 jours</div>
      </div>
      <span class="card-badge">1 JUIN</span>
    </a>

    <a class="card amf disabled">
      <div class="card-icon">🏛️</div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-title">Certification AMF</div>
        <div class="card-sub">Mi-juillet → mi-août 2026 · 3 semaines</div>
      </div>
      <span class="card-badge">MI-JUILLET</span>
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">mathys · boost cv 2026</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
